snippet.title: Puppy Cross Trailer
snippet.description:
Puppy Cross is a Picross game with a twist: as you solve the puzzles you'll unlock content for your garden: dogs, toys, and decorations. Solve some puzzles and customize your cozy little space. Out today on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1183500/Puppy_Cross/
